          "stop_timestamp": "2026-06-25T19:42:20.663108Z",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "**Coffee & walnut cake (8-inch)**\n\nSponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 2 tbsp espresso, 75 g chopped walnuts. Bake 25 min at 180°C.\n\nButtercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1 tbsp espresso.",
