          "text": "No problem — skip the walnuts entirely.\n\n**Coffee cake (8-inch, nut-free)**\n\nSponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 3 tbsp espresso. Bake 25 min at 180°C.\n\nButtercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1½ tbsp espresso. Decorate with chocolate-coated coffee beans instead of walnut halves.",
